---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Acceptable Use Policy — Fimil"
  description="Rules for acceptable use of the Fimil platform."
>
  <article class="py-20 dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/legal" class="text-sm text-fimil-600 hover:text-fimil-700 dark:text-fimil-400"
        >&larr; Legal</a
      >
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Acceptable Use Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Effective Date: March 1, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            1. Permitted Use
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Fimil is intended for scanning your own repositories and code that you have
            authorization to scan.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            2. Prohibited Activities
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            You may not use the Service to scan code you do not own or have permission to scan,
            attempt to circumvent usage limits, reverse engineer the platform, or engage in any
            activity that violates applicable laws.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            3. Enforcement
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Violations may result in suspension or termination of your account. We reserve the right
            to investigate and take appropriate action.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            4. Contact
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Report AUP violations to <a
              href="mailto:abuse@fimil.dev"
              class="text-fimil-600 dark:text-fimil-400">abuse@fimil.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
